    <chapter line="1">2. Akusalapeyyālaṃ</chapter>
    <paragraph line="2" number="191-200"><bold>Sāvajjā</bold>ti <pageBreak edition="V" number="2.0067" /> sadosā. <bold>Anavajjā</bold>ti niddosā. <bold>Dukkhudrayā</bold>ti dukkhavaḍḍhikā. <bold>Sukhudriyā</bold>ti sukhavaḍḍhikā. <bold>Sabyābajjhā</bold>ti sadukkhā. <bold>Abyābajjhā</bold>ti niddukkhā. Ettāvatā vaṭṭavivaṭṭameva kathitaṃ.</paragraph>
    <centered line="3">Akusalapeyyālaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.</centered>
